text.paragraph:
Instructions for measuring the AUC of busulfan at dose 1 (see

                                     Blood Sample Collection for AUC Determination
                                 ) and the formula for adjustment of subsequent doses to achieve the desired target AUC (1125 µM∙min), are provided below.
